To demonstrate our ability to protect sensitive data and ensure compliance with GDPR, we can leverage our ISO 27001 certification, which covers the design, development, and operation of AI-powered information systems. This certification is valid until November 30, 2026, indicating our commitment to maintaining high standards of information security management.

