Lastly, considering our subcontracting policy allows for up to 40% of the contract value to be subcontracted to EU-established entities, after a thorough vetting process, we can explore partnerships with known subcontractors like EuroCloud Solutions S.A. or LexIA GmbH if necessary, to enhance our proposal and meet specific service requirements.

